Tyrael: Rodimus, I presume? I seem to recall you from historical 
databooks.

He transforms, dropping next to the Maximal leader, and stands up.

Tyrael: I don't think we had the opportunity to meet and talk calmly. 
I am Tyrael, Tripredacus Commander on Earth. I hope it will be prove 
to be a pleasure to meet you.

that Tyrael was on.
